      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 21 picture caption about man who was killed after brandishing gun at police officers; incident took place in Shelby, North Carolina, not South Carolina</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption on June 21 about a man who was killed after brandishing guns at police officers outside a station house misidentified the state for Shelby, where the incident occurred. It was North Carolina, not South Carolina.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A picture caption on June 21 about a man who was killed after brandishing guns at police officers outside a station house misidentified the state for Shelby, where the incident occurred. It was North Carolina, not South Carolina.</p>
      </block>
